You will encounter 30 enemies with different abilities and strengths.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.poster.avif?t=1726557690\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.webm?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1664580/extras/6a9d4e721b92a908bfeec0023d0c790c.mp4?t=1726557690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
